OL,3,CFuneral held for baby found under
OL,4,Cfloorboards during renovation
OL,6,FA service has been held to lay the
OL,7,Fbaby, referred to affectionately as
OL,8,F'Baby Auckland', to rest
OL,10,FA funeral has been held for a baby
OL,11,Fwhose remains were discovered under
OL,12,Ffloorboards in a flat in Bishop
OL,13,FAuckland.
OL,15,FThe service for the infant,
OL,16,Faffectionately referred to as 'Baby
OL,17,FAuckland, was led by Durham
OL,18,FConstabulary and Durham County Council
OL,19,Fat Bishop Auckland's Town Cemetery on
OL,20,FMonday (27 April).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
