PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777302667
OL,3,CFuneral held for baby found under
OL,4,Cfloorboards during renovation
OL,6,FThe baby boy's skeletal remains were
OL,7,Ffound by a contractor in an upstairs
OL,8,Fflat on Fore Bondgate on 29 July 2024.
OL,9,FIt had twine around its neck and was
OL,10,Fwrapped in newspaper dating from 1910.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Mel
OL,13,FSutherland, who delivered a tribute
OL,14,Fduring the service, said: "This has
OL,15,Fbeen a deeply thought-provoking case.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777302667
OL,3,CFuneral held for baby found under
OL,4,Cfloorboards during renovation
OL,6,F"Coming together today has allowed us
OL,7,Fto properly acknowledge this little
OL,8,Fboy's life and ensure he was laid to
OL,9,Frest with the dignity and respect he
OL,10,Fdeserved. We hope he may now rest in
OL,11,Fpeace."
OL,13,FThe force launched an investigation
OL,14,Ffollowing the discovery of the baby.
OL,16,FThe infant was found carefully wrapped
OL,17,Fin a newspaper titled 'The Umpire',
OL,18,Fdating back to June 19, 1910, which
OL,19,Fprovided an early line of enquiry as
OL,20,Fofficers examined historical records.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
