OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777302667
OL,3,CFuneral held for baby found under
OL,4,Cfloorboards during renovation
OL,6,FThe baby was taken to the Royal
OL,7,FVictoria Infirmary, in Newcastle,
OL,8,Fwhere a post-mortem examinationJwas
OL,9,Fcarried out. However, a cause of death
OL,10,Fcould not be established.
OL,12,FFurther forensic work, including
OL,13,Fcarbon dating, confirmed the baby was
OL,14,Fmale and dated back to before 1955.
OL,16,FInitial findings also suggested the
OL,17,Fbaby was full-term and his body
OL,18,Fremained undisturbed for many years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
